item.description:
One of the most enlightening classes I have been in recently was with Umesh. He taught that their is great stimulation, relaxation, revelation, and power in meditating. Our class was amazing and I know we want to continue to reach that level of fulfillment.

Please join us this night as we go to a very deep level of mediation. We will discuss briefly chakras and different types of meditation. We will do several mediations and unlock some of the energies that we are holding.

Come with a question you would like to have answered from your inner wisdom.

group.name: Abundance, Empowerment and the Law of Attraction

item.name: Letting Meditation Raise Your Vibration
